{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-10",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_10_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "The Belvedere Divan",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 3,
  "page_total": 5,
  "page_start_sec": 486.752,
  "page_end_sec": 728.36,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.552,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 486.752,
      "end": 488.98,
      "text": "Spade waited until a bespectacled pudgy man",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 488.98,
      "end": 491.5,
      "text": "and a thin-legged blonde girl had passed out"
    },
    {
      "start": 491.5,
      "end": 491.88,
      "text": "of hearing."
    },
    {
      "start": 492.48,
      "end": 493.48,
      "text": "Then he chuckled and said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 494.32,
      "end": 496.62,
      "text": "that would go over big back on Seventh Avenue,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 496.8,
      "end": 497.62,
      "text": "but you're not"
    },
    {
      "start": 497.82,
      "end": 498.68,
      "text": "in Romeville now."
    },
    {
      "start": 498.94,
      "end": 499.94,
      "text": "You're in my burg."
    },
    {
      "start": 500.6,
      "end": 503.54,
      "text": "He exhaled cigarette smoke and blew it out in a long pale",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 503.66,
      "end": 503.9,
      "text": "cloud."
    },
    {
      "start": 504.24,
      "end": 504.34,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 505.38,
      "end": 505.92,
      "text": "where is he?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 506.56,
      "end": 508.06,
      "text": "The boy spoke two words,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 508.46,
      "end": 510.12,
      "text": "the first a short guttural verb,"
    },
    {
      "start": 510.34,
      "end": 511.104,
      "text": "the second you."
    },
    {
      "start": 512.928,
      "end": 514.54,
      "text": "People lose teeth talking like that.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 514.976,
      "end": 516.42,
      "text": "Spade's voice was still amiable,"
    },
    {
      "start": 516.6,
      "end": 517.68,
      "text": "though his face had become"
    },
    {
      "start": 517.8,
      "end": 518.02,
      "text": "wooden."
    },
    {
      "start": 518.94,
      "end": 519.88,
      "text": "If you want to hang around,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 520.12,
      "end": 520.92,
      "text": "you'll be polite."
    },
    {
      "start": 521.28,
      "end": 523.56,
      "text": "The boy repeated his two words."
    },
    {
      "start": 524.768,
      "end": 528.26,
      "text": "Spade dropped his cigarette into a tall stone jar beside the divan",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 528.44,
      "end": 531.04,
      "text": "and with a lifted hand caught the attention of a man"
    },
    {
      "start": 531.52,
      "end": 533.46,
      "text": "who had been standing at an end of"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.46,
      "end": 535.04,
      "text": "the cigar stand for several minutes."
    },
    {
      "start": 535.9,
      "end": 537.62,
      "text": "The man nodded and came towards them.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 538.24,
      "end": 540.2,
      "text": "He was a middle-aged man of medium height,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 540.8,
      "end": 542.2,
      "text": "round and sallow of face,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 542.848,
      "end": 543.58,
      "text": "compactly built,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 544.32,
      "end": 545.72,
      "text": "tidily dressed in dark clothes.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 546.48,
      "end": 546.72,
      "text": "Hello,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 546.76,
      "end": 547.0,
      "text": "Sam,"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.26,
      "end": 548.72,
      "text": "he said as he came up."
    },
    {
      "start": 549.16,
      "end": 549.48,
      "text": "Hello,"
    },
    {
      "start": 549.58,
      "end": 549.86,
      "text": "Luke."
    },
    {
      "start": 550.92,
      "end": 552.22,
      "text": "They shook hands and Luke said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 552.6,
      "end": 554.96,
      "text": "saying that's too bad about miles"
    },
    {
      "start": 555.96,
      "end": 560.2,
      "text": "uh-huh a bad break spade jerked his head to indicate the boy",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 560.2,
      "end": 561.56,
      "text": "on the divan beside him"
    },
    {
      "start": 562.46,
      "end": 565.52,
      "text": "what do you let these cheap gunmen hang out in your lobby for with",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 565.56,
      "end": 569.82,
      "text": "their tools bulging their clothes yes luke examined"
    },
    {
      "start": 569.82,
      "end": 572.56,
      "text": "the boy with crafty brown eyes set in a suddenly"
    },
    {
      "start": 572.68,
      "end": 576.82,
      "text": "hard face what do you want here he asked the boy"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.82,
      "end": 580.26,
      "text": "stood up spade stood up the boy looked at the two"
    },
    {
      "start": 580.44,
      "end": 583.38,
      "text": "men at their neckties from one to the other."
    },
    {
      "start": 584.352,
      "end": 585.44,
      "text": "Luke's necktie was black.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 586.02,
      "end": 586.76,
      "text": "The boy looked like",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 586.76,
      "end": 588.54,
      "text": "a schoolboy standing in front of them."
    },
    {
      "start": 589.472,
      "end": 589.86,
      "text": "Luke said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 590.16,
      "end": 590.26,
      "text": "well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.5,
      "end": 592.48,
      "text": "if you don't want anything,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 592.74,
      "end": 593.472,
      "text": "beat it and"
    },
    {
      "start": 593.68,
      "end": 594.36,
      "text": "don't come back."
    },
    {
      "start": 594.78,
      "end": 595.9,
      "text": "The boy said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 596.14,
      "end": 598.74,
      "text": "I won't forget you guys and went out."
    },
    {
      "start": 599.92,
      "end": 600.92,
      "text": "They watched him go out.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 601.46,
      "end": 603.12,
      "text": "Spade took off his hat and wiped his"
    },
    {
      "start": 603.12,
      "end": 604.56,
      "text": "damp forehead with a handkerchief."
    },
    {
      "start": 604.76,
      "end": 606.68,
      "text": "The hotel detective asked,"
    },
    {
      "start": 606.9,
      "end": 607.62,
      "text": "What is it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 608.704,
      "end": 609.38,
      "text": "Damned if I know,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 609.56,
      "end": 610.12,
      "text": "Spade replied."
    },
    {
      "start": 610.76,
      "end": 611.94,
      "text": "I just happened to spot him.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 612.14,
      "end": 613.26,
      "text": "Know anything about"
    },
    {
      "start": 613.38,
      "end": 614.18,
      "text": "Joel Cairo,"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.34,
      "end": 615.12,
      "text": "635?"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.72,
      "end": 616.52,
      "text": "Oh,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 616.68,
      "end": 617.44,
      "text": "that one,"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.0,
      "end": 619.38,
      "text": "the hotel detective leered.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 620.22,
      "end": 621.18,
      "text": "How long's he been here?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 622.16,
      "end": 622.6,
      "text": "Four days.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 622.72,
      "end": 623.84,
      "text": "This is the fifth."
    },
    {
      "start": 624.84,
      "end": 625.38,
      "text": "What about him?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 626.528,
      "end": 626.84,
      "text": "Search me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 626.92,
      "end": 627.2,
      "text": "Sam."
    },
    {
      "start": 627.72,
      "end": 628.96,
      "text": "I got nothing against him but"
    },
    {
      "start": 628.96,
      "end": 629.46,
      "text": "his looks."
    },
    {
      "start": 630.4,
      "end": 631.84,
      "text": "Find out if he came in last night.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 632.78,
      "end": 633.02,
      "text": "Try to,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 633.26,
      "end": 635.2,
      "text": "the hotel detective promised and went away."
    },
    {
      "start": 635.63,
      "end": 637.9,
      "text": "Spade sat on the divan until he returned."
    },
    {
      "start": 638.3,
      "end": 638.4,
      "text": "No,"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.18,
      "end": 640.1,
      "text": "Luke reported.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 640.58,
      "end": 641.96,
      "text": "He didn't sleep in his room."
    },
    {
      "start": 642.74,
      "end": 643.18,
      "text": "What is it?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 643.8,
      "end": 644.48,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 645.5,
      "end": 646.0,
      "text": "Come clean.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 646.52,
      "end": 647.96,
      "text": "You know I'll keep my clam shut,"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.34,
      "end": 649.44,
      "text": "but if there's anything wrong,"
    },
    {
      "start": 649.56,
      "end": 651.92,
      "text": "we ought to know about it so as we can collect our bill."
    },
    {
      "start": 652.96,
      "end": 653.58,
      "text": "Nothing like that,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 653.72,
      "end": 654.62,
      "text": "Spade assured him."
    },
    {
      "start": 655.08,
      "end": 655.97,
      "text": "As a matter of fact,"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.02,
      "end": 657.56,
      "text": "I'm doing a little work for him."
    },
    {
      "start": 658.1,
      "end": 659.32,
      "text": "I'd tell you if he was wrong."
    },
    {
      "start": 660.48,
      "end": 660.94,
      "text": "You'd better.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 661.58,
      "end": 663.3,
      "text": "Want me to kind of keep an eye on him?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 663.96,
      "end": 664.26,
      "text": "Thanks,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 664.32,
      "end": 664.52,
      "text": "Luke."
    },
    {
      "start": 664.7,
      "end": 665.58,
      "text": "It wouldn't hurt."
    },
    {
      "start": 665.8,
      "end": 669.22,
      "text": "You can't know too much about the men you're working for these days."
    },
    {
      "start": 670.6,
      "end": 674.32,
      "text": "It was 21 minutes past 11 by the clock over the elevator doors",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 674.86,
      "end": 676.42,
      "text": "when Joel Cairo came in from the"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.48,
      "end": 676.64,
      "text": "street."
    },
    {
      "start": 677.6,
      "end": 678.9,
      "text": "His forehead was bandaged.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 679.0,
      "end": 682.44,
      "text": "His clothes had the limp unfreshness of too many hours"
    },
    {
      "start": 682.64,
      "end": 683.58,
      "text": "consecutive wear."
    },
    {
      "start": 683.97,
      "end": 686.76,
      "text": "His face was pasty with sagging mouth and eyelids."
    },
    {
      "start": 687.744,
      "end": 689.24,
      "text": "Spade met him in front of the",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 689.36,
      "end": 689.66,
      "text": "desk."
    },
    {
      "start": 690.34,
      "end": 690.72,
      "text": "Good morning,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 690.96,
      "end": 692.02,
      "text": "Spade said easily."
    },
    {
      "start": 693.152,
      "end": 696.32,
      "text": "Cairo drew his tired body up straight and the drooping lines",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 696.32,
      "end": 697.22,
      "text": "of his face tightened."
    },
    {
      "start": 697.46,
      "end": 698.46,
      "text": "Good morning,"
    },
    {
      "start": 698.62,
      "end": 700.08,
      "text": "he responded without enthusiasm."
    },
    {
      "start": 700.71,
      "end": 702.18,
      "text": "There was a pause.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 703.232,
      "end": 703.8,
      "text": "Spade said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 704.448,
      "end": 706.1,
      "text": "let's go someplace where we can talk.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 707.008,
      "end": 708.18,
      "text": "Cairo raised his chin.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 709.26,
      "end": 710.1,
      "text": "Please excuse me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 710.2,
      "end": 710.64,
      "text": "he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 711.28,
      "end": 713.82,
      "text": "Our conversations in private have not been",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 713.82,
      "end": 716.22,
      "text": "such that I am anxious to continue them."
    },
    {
      "start": 717.472,
      "end": 718.9,
      "text": "Pardon my speaking bluntly,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 719.28,
      "end": 720.22,
      "text": "but it is the truth."
    },
    {
      "start": 721.38,
      "end": 722.3,
      "text": "You mean last night?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 722.912,
      "end": 725.48,
      "text": "Spade made an impatient gesture with head and hands.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 726.62,
      "end": 728.36,
      "text": "What in hell else could I do?",
      "para_break": true
    }
  ]
}